WEBVTT

00:00.322 --> 00:02.620
This has one number on it - mine.

00:02.977 --> 00:04.696
I was given to a man called
Christos.

00:04.697 --> 00:06.218
He taught me how to steal,

00:06.295 --> 00:07.333
how to fight.

00:07.334 --> 00:09.493
They caught him,

00:09.494 --> 00:11.733
tortured him, killed him.

00:11.734 --> 00:14.333
What was my name?

00:14.334 --> 00:16.253
Your name was Pietre.

00:16.254 --> 00:17.293
Get out!

00:17.294 --> 00:19.733
Jesus Christ!

00:19.734 --> 00:21.094
It was chemical poisoning!

00:21.095 --> 00:22.413
Not flu at all!

00:22.414 --> 00:25.614
I have copies with lawyers.
I want Anya released.

00:25.615 --> 00:27.213
I need to see you.

00:27.214 --> 00:28.813
I'm in trouble.

00:28.814 --> 00:30.733
That's not me!

00:30.734 --> 00:31.773
That is not me!

00:31.774 --> 00:35.414
See if he's got the Chinese
character for "rabbit" on his belly.

00:35.415 --> 00:39.414
Then what, whack him?

00:39.654 --> 00:40.893
We go now!

00:40.894 --> 00:42.294
And we take him with us.

00:42.295 --> 00:46.253
I want the manuscript
and you are going to take me to it.

00:46.254 --> 00:49.493
Of course.

00:49.494 --> 00:51.293
That's why I'm here.

